Packages 
Package Description
de.ur.iw.navigame
Main Package for the Navigation Game.
de.ur.iw.navigame.data_download
Area selection and level/storey selection request handlers.
de.ur.iw.navigame.game_logic
Contains parts of the application that predominantly concern actual navigation logic.
de.ur.iw.navigame.server
Parts of the game that deal with web stuff that is specific to this application go here.
de.ur.iw.navigame.sessions
Responsible for creating and loading sessions, which includes selecting start and goal points for the game.
de.ur.iw.navigame.utility
contains several classes that could be used in other web projects.
